      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## Pipeline Summary\n\n- **CI** runs on pushes and pull requests for `main` and `develop`\n- **CD** runs on pushes to `main` and manual dispatch\n- **PR Checks** validate pull requests and apply labels\n- **Dependency Updates** runs weekly and on manual dispatch\n\n### Current Coverage\n\n- Backend CI: `npm ci` and `npm test -- --passWithNoTests`\n- Frontend CI: `npm ci` and `npm run build`\n- Security: backend audit, frontend audit, Trivy scan, SARIF upload\n- Delivery: Docker Buildx publish to **GHCR** for backend and frontend\n\n### Current Gaps\n\n- No automatic Azure deployment from GitHub Actions\n- No real lint scripts wired into CI yet\n- No frontend automated test runner yet\n- Some PR checks are intentionally permissive\n\n### Release Notes\n\n- Runtime images are built for `linux/amd64`\n- Deploy runtime tags like `latest` or SHA tags\n- Do **not** deploy `buildcache`\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "13.0.1",
      "title": "CI/CD Summary",
      "type": "text"
